# Euler's Market Environment Variables

# The Google Apps Script URL for the waitlist form
# To get this: 
# 1. Create a Google Sheet
# 2. Go to Extensions > Apps Script
# 3. Paste the provided backend code
# 4. Deploy > New Deployment > Web App
# 5. Copy the URL and paste it here
VITE_GOOGLE_SCRIPT_URL=YOUR_GOOGLE_APPS_SCRIPT_URL_HERE
